    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable daily driver, though it shows its age. The exterior has several visible paint chips and a few minor door dings, while the interior shows standard wear on the upholstery and some fading on the dashboard plastics. Mechanically, the car runs and drives well, but buyers should anticipate needing new tires and a brake service within the next few months. It's a solid, functional vehicle for someone looking for transportation without the premium price tag of a newer model.",
      "price": 19500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
