    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in absolute mint condition, appearing and driving as if it just rolled off the showroom floor. The exterior paint is flawless with a deep, mirror-like shine and no scratches or dents, while the interior remains pristine with no signs of wear. Mechanically, the car is perfect, having been meticulously maintained with a full service history and all systems functioning exactly as intended. This is a rare find for a collector or a buyer seeking a vehicle in impeccable, factory-standard condition.",
