    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "This vehicle represents a distinguished balance of performance and preservation. Maintained to an exacting standard, it exhibits consistent mechanical reliability and a well-appointed interior. Every primary system has been evaluated to ensure immediate road-readiness and sustained value. This is a premier opportunity to acquire a dependable, high-caliber automobile that upholds the rigorous standards of excellence expected from our inventory.",
      "price": 34800.0,
